coefficient & Action on qubit & Measured value\\\hline
$\lambda_1$ &{\itshape I} & $P_0+P_1$\\\hline
$\lambda _2$ & $R_y\left(-\pi /2\right)$ & $P_0-P_1$\\\hline
$\lambda _3$ & $R_x\left(\pi /2\right)$ & $P_0-P_1$\\\hline
